# frames(in:)

**Instance Method**

All frames within the given time range.

## Declaration

```swift
final func frames(in timeRange: CMTimeRange) -> [CNScript.Frame]
```

## Parameters

- **timeRange**: The time range of interest.

## Return Value

An array of frames within the given time range.
